Package: scReportComposition
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Composition Interactive HTML Report Generator
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Kee-gong Karios",
                  family = "Park",
                  email = "karioslion0517@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate self-contained interactive composition audit reports
    from single-cell RNA-seq data. Upgraded from a composition viewer into a
    descriptive audit tool with sample-level composition, group-level
    descriptive summary, sample dominance detection, and automated warnings.
    No differential composition statistics are performed. Designed as a
    lightweight companion to scReportLite in the scReport ecosystem.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    plotly,
    htmltools,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    Seurat,
    SeuratObject
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
